T02TD2856E:196a-1: shr'i kharsa pa na lo ki shva ra s'adha nam /
T02TD2856E:196a-3: dpal kharsa pan 'jig rten dbang phyug gi sgrub thabs /
T02TD2856E:196a-4: thugs rje chen po 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2856E:196a-5: rnal 'byor dbang phyug byams pa dang //
T02TD2856E:196a-6: snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms las //
T02TD2856E:196a-7: byung ba'i byang chub sems kyi bdag /'jig rten mgon po la phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2856E:196a-8: de zhabs padmo la reg pas //
T02TD2856E:196a-9: 'jig rten sdug bsngal bsgral ba'i phyir //
T02TD2856E:196a-10: ji bzhin ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD2856E:196a-11: mdor bsdus bdag gis bstan par bya //
T02TD2856E:196a-12: mkha' ltar dri med stong nyid dbyings las dbang po gzhu ltar gsal ba'i dngos //
T02TD2856E:196a-13: padmo zla rgyas thugs gsung 'od 'phro sgyu ma'i rnam thar sprul pa'i sku //
T02TD2856E:196a-14: rab mdzes sku ni gzi brjid brtan mdzes 'bar ba'i 'od zer dkar 'khrigs pa //
T02TD2856E:196a-15: skyil krung phyed brkyang dul ba'i phyag g-yas mchod sbyin gsal po g-yon gyi phyag / padma'i sdong mdzes dri med 'dab rgyas gzhon nu sgeg po'i thugs kar 'dzin //
T02TD2856E:196a-16: shel ltar dri med autpal spyan ring kun nas yid 'phrog 'od 'bar zhal //
T02TD2856E:196a-17: brtan po dkar gsal zla rgyas stong lhag ral pa'i cod pan thub pa'i gdan //
T02TD2856E:196b-0: 'bar ba'i @196b rin chen dri med sna tshogs shin tu 'od sbyangs legs spras shing //
T02TD2856E:196b-1: mkha' la nyi shar lham me lhan ne nam mkha'i mthar gtugs 'od 'gyed pa //
T02TD2856E:196b-2: dpe byad mtshan rdzogs gcig pu skyob pa skyabs kyi dam pa slu med de //
T02TD2856E:196b-3: shin tu rtogs dkar de nyid gzhir gyur snying gi pad 'dab hr'i: yig gis //
T02TD2856E:196b-4: gang ba'i phyogs rnams de bzhin de gzugs aom dang a'a: dang hr'i: dang h'um //
T02TD2856E:196b-5: dkar sogs kha dog dag gi phreng ba yid ni ye shes yig 'bru'i dngos //
T02TD2856E:196b-6: brtse pa'i rlung bskyod ye shes me 'bar 'gro ba'i sdig tshogs bud shing bsregs //
T02TD2856E:196b-7: zhi ba'i ngang ni gnyis med mi g-yo mkha' ltar spros bral ro gcig ro //
T02TD2856E:196b-8: bde chen 'byung gnas ye shes dri med mnyam gzhag chen po bsgom par bya //
T02TD2856E:196b-9: de rjes mchod sogs dag pa'i yan lag cho ga ji bzhin ye shes sems dpa' legs bcug ste //
T02TD2856E:196b-10: rnam gsum 'khor lo dkar dmar sngo tshul go rims bzhin du sku gsung thugs //
T02TD2856E:196b-11: brtan po'i mtshan nyid dam pa'i zhal bzhin mkhas pas rab tu shes par bya //
T02TD2856E:196b-12: thugs rje chen po kharsa pan'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2856E:196b-13: grub pa brnyes pa'i skyes bu chen po shr'i sh'anta ka ras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2856E:196b-15: // / bod kyi lo ts'a ba gnubs byams pa'i dpal gyis bsgyur ba'o//
